@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container mt-4">
    <h1 class="mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p class="text-muted">
        Last Updated: February 2026
    </p>

    <hr />

    <h4>1. Introduction</h4>
    <p>
        StudentManagementSystem is committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring
        the security of your personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how
        we collect, use, and safeguard data within our system.
    </p>

    <h4>2. Information We Collect</h4>
    <p>
        We may collect the following types of information:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Student details such as name, email address, and age</li>
        <li>Administrator account information</li>
        <li>System usage and authentication logs</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>3. How We Use Information</h4>
    <p>
        The information collected is used strictly for:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Managing student records</li>
        <li>Authenticating authorized users</li>
        <li>Improving system functionality and security</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>4. Data Security</h4>
    <p>
        We implement industry-standard security measures including encrypted
        authentication, secure database access, and role-based authorization
        to protect your information.
    </p>

    <h4>5. Data Sharing</h4>
    <p>
        We do not sell, trade, or share personal information with third parties.
        Access to data is strictly limited to authorized administrators.
    </p>

    <h4>6. Cookies & Session Data</h4>
    <p>
        This application may use secure authentication cookies to maintain
        login sessions and ensure authorized access to protected resources.
    </p>

    <h4>7. Changes to This Policy</h4>
    <p>
        We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time.
        Updates will be reflected on this page with a revised "Last Updated" date.
    </p>
        
    <h4>8. Contact Information</h4>
    <p>
        For any questions regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact the system administrator.
    </p>
</div>